    <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl font-bold grad-text sm:text-4xl">Four Categories of GEO Tooling</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">
      The GEO tool landscape splits into four functional categories, each addressing a distinct part of the AI visibility problem. Mature programmes use tools from all four. Brands starting out typically begin with an AI visibility tracker and add capability as their programme matures.
    </p>

